name: Blue and Ivory Flower and Polka Dot print Large Pleated Sling Bag with 4 inside pockets
description:
Large sling bag made with 3 different coordinating prints of navy, light blue and ivory colors that make this bag something everyone notices! Interfaced and topstitched, this bag will stand up on it's own. Put it over your shoulder and you can hold a lot of stuff! Makes a great diaper bag for a hip mom. Easy shape makes it simple to get things in and out of. Bag is approximately 18 in long, by approximately 15 in wide and a 4 in gusset at the bottom which is nicely curved to make it very stylish. Strap is about 12 in drop. 4 Pockets inside the pouch made with coordinating material.
*Items/Accessories shown in pictures with bags are not included*
